      "rationale": "Validation performed on the exact non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design intended for submission, under the exact ASTM F1717 test configuration specified in the COU. No geometric surrogates or scaled models used. Loading and boundary conditions identical between validation and COU. Gradation 3 achieved."
